events.name: Milwaukee Bucks at San Antonio Spurs

headlines.description: — The first battle between Milwaukee Bucks superstar Giannis Antetokounmpo and San Antonio Spurs rookie sensation Victor Wembanyama exceeded the hype.
headlines.shortLinkText: Antetokounmpo has 44 points, 14 rebounds, Bucks overcome Wembanyama, Spurs, 125-121

events.name: Denver Nuggets at Golden State Warriors

headlines.description: — With three seconds left in a tie game, Denver Nuggets coach Michael Malone set up Nikola Jokic to be the safety valve on an inbounds pass at the far end. Jamal Murray, the first option, wasn't available up the sideline. Neither was second-choice...
headlines.shortLinkText: Nikola Jokic hits 40-footer at buzzer, Nuggets rally to stun Warriors 130-127
